---
title: Apricot-Glazed Pork Meatballs with Potato Fries & Carrot Slaw
description: Your favourite plump little orange fruit has been turned into a sauce and wrapped around tender chermoula-spiced pork meatballs to add a burst of sweetness. Paired with classic potato fries and a crunchy slaw, you can’t go wrong!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604d5990d5f299b40db8281-419b4bce.jpeg
